---

<section id="about" class="py-20 px-4 relative" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <div class="ascii-box inline-block mb-4">
        <span class="text-amber-500">$</span> cat about.md
      </div>
      <h2 id="about-heading" class="section-title">Über mich</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
      <!-- Text content -->
      <div class="space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          Ich bin David, <span class="text-amber-500 font-semibold">Full-Stack Developer</span> aus Bad Hersfeld.
          Seit über 5 Jahren baue ich Web-Applikationen — vom schnellen MVP bis zur ausgereiften Architektur, die auch morgen noch funktioniert.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          Bei der <span class="text-emerald-400 font-semibold">DBE-Academy</span> gebe ich mein Wissen weiter.
          Keine langweiligen Slides, keine theoretischen Beispiele — ich zeige, wie man wirklich gute Software baut.
          Die Studenten CODEN, deployed wird auch. 🍻
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          Aktuell beschäftige ich mich intensiv mit <span class="text-amber-500 font-semibold">AI/MLOps</span> —
          Agentic AI, RAG-Architekturen, LLMs in bestehende Systeme einbauen. Das Feld bewegt sich schnell.
          Ich auch.
        </p>

        <!-- GitHub Stats -->
        <div class="border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 pt-6 mt-6">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-500 font-mono mb-4" aria-hidden="true">// GitHub Stats</p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4">
            <a href="https://github.com/davidschuchert" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-xl hover:bg-amber-50 dark:hover:bg-amber-900/20 transition-colors min-h-[70px] justify-center" aria-label="GitHub Followers ansehen">
              <img src="https://img.shields.io/github/followers/DavidSchuchert?style=flat-square&label=Followers" alt="GitHub Followers Badge" class="h-6 mb-1" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">Followers</span>
            </a>
            <a href="https://github.com/DavidSchuchert?tab=repositories" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-xl hover:bg-amber-50 dark:hover:bg-amber-900/20 transition-colors min-h-[70px] justify-center" aria-label="GitHub Stars und Repositories ansehen">
              <img src="https://img.shields.io/github/stars/DavidSchuchert?style=flat-square&label=Stars" alt="GitHub Stars Badge" class="h-6 mb-1" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">Stars</span>
            </a>
            <a href="https://github.com/DavidSchuchert" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex flex-col items-center p-3 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-xl hover:bg-amber-50 dark:hover:bg-amber-900/20 transition-colors min-h-[70px] justify-center" aria-label="Verwendete Programmiersprachen auf GitHub ansehen">
              <img src="https://img.shields.io/github/languages/count/DavidSchuchert/DavidSchuchert?style=flat-square&label=Languages" alt="Anzahl verwendeter Programmiersprachen Badge" class="h-6 mb-1" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">Languages</span>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4">
            <img src="https://github-readme-stats.vercel.app/api/top-langs/?username=DavidSchuchert&layout=compact&theme=amber&hide_border=false" alt="Am häufigsten verwendete Programmiersprachen auf meinen GitHub Repositories" class="rounded-lg" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Fun facts -->
        <div class="border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 pt-6 mt-6">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-500 font-mono mb-3" aria-hidden="true">// Status: Gaming-Setup aktiviert 🎮</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-amber-500" aria-hidden="true">🍻</span> Bad Hersfeld, Germany
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-emerald-400" aria-hidden="true">⚡</span> Schreibt Code, der auch morgen noch lesbar ist
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-amber-500" aria-hidden="true">📚</span> AI/MLOps — wo Systeme dazulernen
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-emerald-400" aria-hidden="true">🎮</span> Kann mit einer Hand am Controller coden — theoretisch
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ASCII Art Character Card -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="ascii-box p-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-100 to-gray-50 dark:from-gray-900 dark:to-gray-950 border-amber-200 dark:border-amber-900" role="img" aria-label="ASCII Art Visitenkarte: David Schuchert — Gaming-Opa, Full-Stack Dev, DBE-Academy Dozent, AI/MLOps Explorer. Passion enabled.">
          <pre class="text-sm leading-tight text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 font-mono" aria-hidden="true">
    ╔══════════════════════════╗
    ║  <span class="text-amber-500">David Schuchert</span>       ║
    ╠══════════════════════════╣
    ║  🎮 Gaming-Opa          ║
    ║  💻 Full-Stack Dev      ║
    ║  🎓 DBE-Academy Dozent ║
    ║  🤖 AI/MLOps Explorer  ║
    ║                          ║
    ║  [##########] 100%       ║
    ║  Passion enabled         ║
    ╚══════════════════════════╝
          </pre>
          <div class="mt-4 flex justify-center gap-2" aria-label="Interessen">
            <span class="text-2xl hover:scale-110 transition-transform cursor-pointer" title="Code" aria-hidden="true">💻</span>
            <span class="text-2xl hover:scale-110 transition-transform cursor-pointer" title="Gaming" aria-hidden="true">🎮</span>
            <span class="text-2xl hover:scale-110 transition-transform cursor-pointer" title="Bier" aria-hidden="true">🍻</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
